{"title":"兵士的心","authors":["王辽生"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵士的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王辽生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵士的心是奇特的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时很软，有时很硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"软时一如娓娓轻风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"害怕伤了小草的生命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬时一如团团大火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对祖国的敌人毫不留情。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}